text: Ernesto del Castillo (born 21 November 1929) was a Mexican equestrian. He competed in two events at the 1968 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1929 births Category:Possibly living people Category:Mexican male equestrians Category:Olympic equestrians of Mexico Category:Equestrians at the 1968 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Veracruz Category:People from Tuxpan, Veracruz
